Â§ quick-start
commands:
list                    : show all available jutsu
exit                    : quit the program
[jutsu name]            : perform the specified jutsu

configuration:
termjutsu is designed to be simple and extensible. new jutsu can be added by modifying the arrays in the source code:
    JUTSU_PATTERNS - for emoji patterns
    JUTSU_JAPANESE - for japanese names

running termjutsu:
    ./termjutsu.sh
or add to your path:
    sudo cp termjutsu.sh /usr/local/bin/termjutsu
    termjutsu

